    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TWA\nTIMETABLE\nEFFECTIVE JANUARY 11-FEBRUARY 28, 1982\nBig news in big seats.\nTWA's new coast-to-coast\nAmbassador Class.™\nTWA\n\"TWA's new business class has\nenough room for anybody.\nEven a big guy like Kareem.\nWilt Chamberlain 7'1\"\n\"Yeah and if I'm comfortable\nimagine how comfortable a\nlittle guy like Wilt is\"\nKareem Abdul Jabbar 7'2\"\nEnjoy more comfort in TWA's new Ambassador Class.\nFewer and wider seats.\nComplimentary cocktails and wine.\nA separate business class section.\nA special Introductory Offer -earn double mileage\ncredit in our Frequent Flight Bonus'™ program.\nNow available on all nonstop\ntranscontinental flights.",
      "SEATTLE/TACOMA\nBOSTON\nSALTLAKE CITY\nADELFTIF\nTON RAIMORE\nLOS ANGELE\n\u0026 TULSA LITTLE ROCK\nOKLAHOMA CITY\nALBUQUERQUE AMARILLO\nSAN DIEGI\nSAN ANTONTO\nNEST PALM BEACH\nFORT LAUDERDALE\nNALAM\nLONDON\nFRANKFURT\nMILAN\nLISBON\nMADRID\nBARCELONA\nTRANS WORLD ROUTES\nTWAH\n• TEL AVIV"
    ],
